{"TopicId":136423,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"What is the red light by the VSI for?","CreatedByName":"EivlEvo","CreatedById":158024,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-08T17:00:18Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"EivlEvo","CreatedById":158024,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-08T17:00:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnybody know this? I\u0027m a real pilot and it\u0027s driving me mad!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Galileo","CreatedById":150430,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-08T17:24:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI dunno exactly but I\u00A0think Hulk Hogan asked the same question and never got an answer. It turned out ok for him though \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-08T17:26:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich cockpit are we talking about?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA screenshot would help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI fly too!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhomphaia","CreatedById":2440,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-08T18:02:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRed for danger. \u00A0If your descent\u00A0exceeds 12m/s (I think, Hard to read that fine on the VSI)\u00A0it lights up.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wemb","CreatedById":121979,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-12T13:28:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nExtra drama?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/jZn1fhMdrbQ?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-12T13:30:36Z\u0022 title=\u002204/12/2016 01:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 12, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Wemb\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EivlEvo","CreatedById":158024,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-13T16:11:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222502628\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460136374\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 4/8/2016 at 1:26 PM, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich cockpit are we talking about?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nA screenshot would help.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI fly too!\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust the external view thingy. At the top center of the screen where it shows your altitude.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-14T04:31:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis one?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bpSs0tN.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022bpSs0tN.png\u0022\u003E \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeans you are descending at a potentially hazardous speed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"EivlEvo","CreatedById":158024,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-14T15:37:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222513093\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460608272\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n11 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis one?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022bpSs0tN.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/bpSs0tN.png\u0022\u003E \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMeans you are descending at a potentially hazardous speed.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVanamonde! Cool... do we know what the triangle above it is? I see it change from red to blue?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rhomphaia","CreatedById":2440,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-14T19:05:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222513678\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022136423\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460648244\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022158024\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022EivlEvo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, EivlEvo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nVanamonde! Cool... do we know what the triangle above it is? I see it change from red to blue?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe triangle indicates whether you can safely return to the space center (blue) or recover the vessel (green)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}